02:11:35.199 --> 02:11:37.669
down walls. Thank you, Lord, there

02:11:37.669 --> 02:11:37.679
is

02:11:37.679 --> 02:11:39.990
peace and joy over

02:11:39.990 --> 02:11:40.000
Barron,

02:11:40.000 --> 02:11:41.750
and

02:11:41.760 --> 02:11:44.709
Father, that he'll find you. Same

02:11:44.719 --> 02:11:47.990
with Ivanka, same with Tiffany,

02:11:48.000 --> 02:11:51.830
Eric, and Don Jr. We pray for a

02:11:51.840 --> 02:11:54.310
revival in that family

02:11:54.320 --> 02:11:57.109
in Jesus'name. We

02:11:57.119 --> 02:12:01.350
call healing over

02:12:01.360 --> 02:12:03.910
Vanessa,

02:12:03.920 --> 02:12:07.510
Don Jr's ex-wife. Breast cancer is gone and it's

02:12:07.510 --> 02:12:07.520
not in the bone. We call

02:12:07.520 --> 02:12:10.149
healing over her

02:12:16.719 --> 02:12:19.430
body and thank you, Lord, that

02:12:19.440 --> 02:12:21.430
she's delivered and whole.

02:12:21.440 --> 02:12:23.589
Those kids

02:12:23.599 --> 02:12:26.069
will not be alone; everything's going to

02:12:26.079 --> 02:12:28.149
be okay.

02:12:42.159 --> 02:12:45.910
We pray over

02:12:45.920 --> 02:12:48.550
President Trump's birthday and

02:12:48.560 --> 02:12:50.629
the games and the World Cup

02:12:50.639 --> 02:12:53.430
starting

02:12:53.440 --> 02:12:55.750
tomorrow,

02:12:55.760 --> 02:12:57.510
the

02:12:57.520 --> 02:13:00.390
11th,

02:13:00.400 --> 02:13:02.950
in Los Angeles.

02:13:05.440 --> 02:13:07.350
I believe

02:13:07.360 --> 02:13:09.430
I could keep pushing

02:13:09.440 --> 02:13:11.830
for three hours, but it's

02:13:11.840 --> 02:13:14.229
not necessary. You can watch yesterday's

02:13:14.239 --> 02:13:16.629
video and we'll

02:13:16.639 --> 02:13:18.390
be back to keep interceding for

02:13:18.400 --> 02:13:21.669
the nations.

02:13:37.119 --> 02:13:39.350
I tried to pray more and not talk so

02:13:39.360 --> 02:13:40.950
much

02:13:40.950 --> 02:13:40.960
today,

02:13:40.960 --> 02:13:43.350
but there's always a river to flow down.

02:14:02.320 --> 02:14:03.990
I'm just thankful for every single one

02:14:04.000 --> 02:14:07.830
of you

02:14:10.000 --> 02:14:13.589
showing

02:14:18.800 --> 02:14:20.950
up every day

02:14:20.950 --> 02:14:20.960
to

02:14:20.960 --> 02:14:23.189
pray with me.

02:14:23.199 --> 02:14:25.910
Many hands make light work,

02:14:25.910 --> 02:14:25.920
and

02:14:25.920 --> 02:14:27.750
I appreciate

02:14:27.760 --> 02:14:30.390
every single one of you. I

02:14:30.390 --> 02:14:30.400
am

02:14:30.400 --> 02:14:34.069
so grateful for you. The pressure that

02:14:34.069 --> 02:14:34.079
I tried

02:14:34.079 --> 02:14:35.990
to tell you all about yesterday is that when

02:14:36.000 --> 02:14:38.069
you lead,

02:14:38.079 --> 02:14:39.750
there's something so different than

02:14:39.760 --> 02:14:42.069
leading in a prayer group. When

02:14:42.079 --> 02:14:44.390
you're leading and you feel the

02:14:44.400 --> 02:14:46.390
pull, it's like a boat

02:14:46.400 --> 02:14:47.910
anchor.

02:14:47.920 --> 02:14:49.750
It's like when you see those big massive

02:14:49.760 --> 02:14:51.189
chains and you're pulling it up out of

02:14:51.199 --> 02:14:52.950
the water, and the

02:14:52.950 --> 02:14:52.960
anchor is

02:14:52.960 --> 02:14:55.350
massive on a huge boat like a

02:14:55.360 --> 02:14:58.229
big cruise ship. It's like pulling a

02:14:58.239 --> 02:15:00.149
chain; you're pulling in the spirit

02:15:00.159 --> 02:15:02.790
realm. I can feel it because we're

02:15:02.800 --> 02:15:05.350
praying for the nations. It's not

02:15:05.360 --> 02:15:06.870
just like, 'Well, Father, I think you're

02:15:06.880 --> 02:15:08.229
praying for my family and you're showing

02:15:08.239 --> 02:15:10.229
me things around.'This

02:15:10.229 --> 02:15:10.239
is

02:15:10.239 --> 02:15:11.910
corporate;

02:15:11.920 --> 02:15:13.669
I can feel it when it comes out.

02:15:13.679 --> 02:15:15.750
Whenever the Lord spoke last night, He

02:15:15.760 --> 02:15:17.750
said,

02:15:17.750 --> 02:15:17.760
'Push.'I

02:15:17.760 --> 02:15:19.030
could hear Him; He was

02:15:19.040 --> 02:15:22.310
audible: 'Push, push, push.'I knew

02:15:22.320 --> 02:15:24.149
what He was saying: 'You've got to push

02:15:24.159 --> 02:15:26.470
above this; you've got to go above the

02:15:26.470 --> 02:15:26.480
hill.'And

02:15:26.480 --> 02:15:27.750
that's what He's doing tonight.

02:15:27.760 --> 02:15:29.589
I told her, I said, 'Pray.'I can

02:15:29.599 --> 02:15:31.510
feel when my wife's helping me pray. You

02:15:31.520 --> 02:15:35.669
could push above it. There

02:15:35.669 --> 02:15:35.679
are

02:15:35.679 --> 02:15:37.030
things He wants to show you; there

02:15:37.030 --> 02:15:37.040
are

02:15:37.040 --> 02:15:39.750
things that need to be uncovered.

02:15:39.760 --> 02:15:43.430
Hallelujah! For many hands make

02:15:43.440 --> 02:15:45.750
light work. Isn't that wonderful? We're

02:15:45.760 --> 02:15:47.830
all a body, moving together.

02:15:47.840 --> 02:15:49.430
We're here tonight and we're so

02:15:49.440 --> 02:15:51.350
thankful for every single one of you. It

02:15:51.360 --> 02:15:53.990
just turned midnight in Central America.

02:15:54.000 --> 02:15:56.709
God bless you all. We love you.

02:15:56.719 --> 02:15:59.510
Enjoy your Thursday and we'll be

02:15:59.520 --> 02:16:00.950
back with you. We'll keep praying,

02:16:00.960 --> 02:16:03.350
keep believing, and doing what

02:16:03.360 --> 02:16:06.310
we're called to do, one soul at a time,

02:16:06.320 --> 02:16:07.910
all doing what Jesus has called us to

02:16:07.920 --> 02:16:09.350
do, pushing and marching forward.

02:16:09.360 --> 02:16:11.910
Soldiers, thank you for being here.

02:16:11.920 --> 02:16:16.069
Remember: put a smile on your face and a

02:16:16.079 --> 02:16:19.030
song in your heart. Jesus loves you so

02:16:19.040 --> 02:16:21.350
much and we love you. God bless you and

02:16:21.360 --> 02:16:25.360
we'll see you again. Bye-bye.

